Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,请听我今天的忏悔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友们…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是…
